{"tid":849866,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★大量iPhone XS用戶使用幾天後揚聲器無法工作 ，Apple：不可能修復這個問題","createTime":"2018-10-06T04:37:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T07:02:11.000Z","uid":19454,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4892bf94c25770fa9a7bd42dc21ae0661478a6b7","tid":849866,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T04:37:14.000Z","msg":"10月5日消息，來自《福布斯》雜誌的一篇評論講到，雖然用戶們非常喜歡蘋果的新iPhone XS和iPhone XS Max，但蘋果悄然承認他們的新手機出現了嚴重的充電問題。現在一份新的調查報告顯示充電問題不是蘋果新手機的唯一缺陷。<br />\n<br />\n據報導稱，<span style=\"color: red;\">大量的iPhone XS和iPhone XS Max用戶報告說他們手機上的揚聲器無法正常工作。此外，看起來短時間之內蘋果不太可能會修復這個問題。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n具體來講，報導引用了國外著名論壇網站Reddit，以及Twitter、蘋果官方支持社區、粉絲網站iMore和其他多個網站上的用戶報告，蘋果手機的用戶在這些網站上表示他們的iPhone XS和iPhone XS Max的頂部揚聲器會在播放音樂時停止工作。<br />\n<br />\n有一個用戶在推特上抱怨道：&ldquo;iPhone XS使用耳機揚聲器和底部揚聲器來創造立體聲效果，使用iPhone XS Max幾天后，耳機揚聲器就停止工作了。<span style=\"color: red;\">重啟手機似乎解決了這個問題。但是沒過多久問題就會重演。&ldquo;</span><br />\n<br />\n在另一個受影響的用戶發布的視頻中可以清楚地看到手機揚聲器的問題。<br />\n<br />\n奇怪的是，電話功能沒有受到這個問題的影響，這是個好消息，因為這幾乎斷定故障是軟件相關的而不是硬件問題。也就是說，雖然需要等待一段時間但是這個問題還是可以通過軟件更新來的修復的。一個受影響的用戶表示更新到最新的iOS 12.1測試版沒有解決揚聲器的問題。<br />\n<br />\n福布斯網站已經聯繫了蘋果公司，去詢問該公司對此問題的看法。但是<span style=\"color: red;\">目前還沒有收到蘋果公司的回應。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com/0/387/033.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com%2F0%2F387%2F033.htm&d=UOe6E5NqDY%2Bf96mpHv%2FyZ4M9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=22c536e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com/0/387/033.htm</a>"},{"pid":"45475372059599102bba9fed99dd64d8607f14be","tid":849866,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T04:37:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cfad669dce1bf6e7a9b9ed6168d585481855c38","tid":849866,"uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T04:37:57.000Z","msg":"短時間之內蘋果不太可能會修復這個問題。<br />\n短時間之內蘋果不太可能會修復這個問題。<br />\n短時間之內蘋果不太可能會修復這個問題。"},{"pid":"ec7dee144b03da8043c58e0eac3793a0fa3ec8f2","tid":849866,"uid":24660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"45475372059599102bba9fed99dd64d8607f14be","tid":849866,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T04:37:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T04:38:06.000Z","msg":"笑甚麼，你也是idog"},{"pid":"963bdb1509370525c0ff1368ec329044b6286f37","tid":849866,"uid":33523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T04:38:33.000Z","msg":"用家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7886c25bb950c14d35118d86292266ff5a1e9bb","tid":849866,"uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T04:38:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Gay Cook : Bad Phone ,Bad Luck</span>"},{"pid":"e70cd040df10b0632517c27ece6fdb923d1f1c13","tid":849866,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T04:40:43.000Z","msg":"香港冇得refund<br />\n<br />\n次貨必先運港出售<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c50357f42f7e0409251148013ce7106435bedc67","tid":849866,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T04:43:05.000Z","msg":"白老鼠"},{"pid":"b0ca1442b0de15217bcb27d4fdf6819874310e70","tid":849866,"uid":4330,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"cite